org.apache.chemistry.opencmis.client.api

Interface CmisObject

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CmisObjectProperties, ObjectId
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Document, FileableCmisObject, Folder, Item, Policy, Relationship

    public interface CmisObject
extends ObjectId, CmisObjectProperties
    Base interface for all CMIS objects.

      • updateProperties

        Parameters:
        properties - the properties to update
        refresh - true if this object should be refresh after the update, false if not
        Returns:
        the object ID of the updated object

        1.0
